(* Proof:
   Note n < (SUC (SQRT n)) ** 2                by SQRT_PROPERTY
          = SUC ((SQRT n) ** 2) + 2 * SQRT n   by SUC_SQ
   Thus n <= m ** 2 + 2 * m                    by SQRT n <= m
          <= m ** 2 + 2 * m ** 2               by arithmetic
