       Let m = n - 1.
       Note 0 < m                          by 1 < n
        ==> m < 2 ** SUC (LOG2 m)          by LOG2_PROPERTY, 0 < m
        n - 1 < 2 ** SUC (LOG2 m)          by notation
            n <= 2 ** SUC (LOG2 m)         by inequality [2]
         or n <= 2 ** SUC (LOG2 (n - 1))   by notation
