   Let mb = ppidx b, qb = b DIV p ** mb.
   Then coprime p qa             by prime_power_cofactor_coprime
       gcd p (gcd qa qb)
     = gcd (gcd p qa) qb         by GCD_ASSOC
     = gcd 1 qb                  by coprime p qa
