(* Theorem: MAX_SET (less_divisors n) <= n DIV 2 *)
(* Proof:
   Let s = less_divisors n, m = MAX_SET s.
   If s = {},
      Then m = MAX_SET {} = 0          by MAX_SET_EMPTY
       and 0 <= n DIV 2 is trivial.
   If s <> {},
